            Not sure why Goretzka was played so far forward when he is already an excellent box-to-box midfielder and Bayern are superb at controlling the middle of the park. Playing him next to Bentaleb wouldn't have changed the result but I thought it was a strange decision to start him as an inside forward/attacking midfielder given how great he has been thus far this season as a box-to-box CM. My guess is he will be in the midfield for Schalke's next game.
